00:20:49,097 --> 00:20:51,227
Well, looks like
you're gonna have

439
00:20:51,234 --> 00:20:53,614
to keep this a bowling alley.

440
00:20:53,606 --> 00:20:56,506
A very popular alley,
which I now own.

441
00:20:56,512 --> 00:20:59,852
I'm gonna make it one lane only
with a three-month waiting list.

442
00:20:59,852 --> 00:21:02,362
Hipsters rule.

443
00:21:02,356 --> 00:21:05,896
Oh, Marge, you saved my alley,
you saved my ego.

444
00:21:05,897 --> 00:21:07,567
You do love me after all.

445
00:21:07,568 --> 00:21:10,208
Was there ever any doubt?

